transcription: On Tuesday, November 7th, cast your vote for Tanya Bamford and Matthew Quaig for Supervisor. With decades of business experience and extensive community involvement, Bamford and Quaig have the integrity, leadership, and experience we need to lead Montgomery Township effectively. Remember to vote on Tuesday, November 7th for Bamford and Quaig for Montgomery Township Supervisor.  My name is Tanya Bamford and I approve this message.
